✴ Portrait of Anti

Anti was made from smoke and volcanoes. It produces black smoke breath. The others then ask, why are you so angry all the time? 

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consist of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
